8622,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea9fd9656908eb7a7692374e60fccfc8378348aa","tid":868622,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf377463128d8497f023ae5717f01fbc0f6e522","tid":868622,"uid":118553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"882d5fe185a3ac00af204fa0e2f2d6a854a35d52","tid":868622,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打想做果D係咩黎架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"主要都係自己有興趣嘅嘢，有時咁啱見到有展覽/電影想去睇，但係就成日畀返工忙、要做功課呢啲藉口自己而冇去做/plan幾時去做<br />\n放假又成日hea同瞓，結果到諗起想睇嗰啲嘢嘅時候人哋個展覽都完咗/套戲落咗畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時我覺得係香港人真係太忙...<br />\n返工又OT, 要話要增值多D咁, 搞到個人好攰..<br />\n放工就想休息<br />\n想做其他野都無乜動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:35:44.000Z","msg":"唔否認好多香港人真係忙到一啲私人時間都冇嘅<br />\n但係我覺得自己只係懶，同唔識安排好自己時間先搞到咁...<br />\n我認為放假嗰陣去做啲自己想做嘅事先係真正嘅休息，但結果次次都瞓到黃朝白晏，又賴床唔肯起身<br />\n好憎自己浪費曬啲時間，有假期都唔㚥好利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7c181ac1870e4080a8ce55141f49de475b6673","tid":868622,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ce683e8af0d3580d6e6966bb9de328c3e59e9f2","tid":868622,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"懶唔係問題<br />\n蠢先係問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但一個人聰明即使佢好懶佢係會不斷諗辦法令自己繼續懶而同樣都可以完成到件事<br />\n<br />\n相反蠢既跟本唔識諗自己做緊既方向係岩定錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"巴打都講得有啲道理，有能力嘅人係有辦法可以畀自己懶得嚟又完成到件事或甚至有更高效率<br />\n最近都諗梗係咪跟本自己能力唔高先搞到好似做咩事都做唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6209366e41f385a3a485054f9e7de6a3f0f73b13","tid":868622,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f7c181ac1870e4080a8ce55141f49de475b6673","tid":868622,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ce683e8af0d3580d6e6966bb9de328c3e59e9f2","tid":868622,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"懶唔係問題<br />\n蠢先係問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但一個人聰明即使佢好懶佢係會不斷諗辦法令自己繼續懶而同樣都可以完成到件事<br />\n<br />\n相反蠢既跟本唔識諗自己做緊既方向係岩定錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"巴打都講得有啲道理，有能力嘅人係有辦法可以畀自己懶得嚟又完成到件事或甚至有更高效率<br />\n最近都諗梗係咪跟本自己能力唔高先搞到好似做咩事都做唔好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T17:47:44.000Z","msg":"樓上巴打講都有D道理<br />\n不過我又覺得要睇埋對做某一樣野有幾大決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n約左CARE既人, 一定會著靚D同早D出門口 ..果時又唔會懶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0530f8b63bd0eeb2445619f53609773931623f6a","tid":868622,"uid":142247,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:12:45.000Z","msg":"最近睇完本書係講拖延嘅<br />\n有啲建議可以影俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ptUy4gY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FptUy4gY.jpg&h=f7587627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWFVyag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWFVyag.jpg&h=7c25264c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x0dzOJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0dzOJA.jpg&h=7d12be43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q8bmtJy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq8bmtJy.jpg&h=278cd7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n共勉之啦<br />\n<br />\n其實我睇完本書都冇話有冇好大嘅啟發令我去改善<br />\n但「千里之行，始於足下」<br />\n呢一刻你唔去改<br />\n你一世都只會係咁<br />\n<br />\n佢仲有一種方法我覺得值得試一下<br />\n大概係首先畫個一星期嘅timetable<br />\n將你下星期已知道唔得閒嘅時候填咗佢<br />\n睇下剩番幾多時間可以做嘢<br />\n無論十五分鐘定幾個鐘都好<br />\n係嗰啲空白嘅時間做你要做嘢<br />\n嗰個section唔夠時間嘅話就試下將個task拆開嚟做<br />\n做咗最輕鬆最快搞點嗰part佢<br />\n<br />\n最重要係每日keep住track自己嘅進度<br />\n同埋搵啲嘢鼓勵下自己<br />\n例如睇場戲 打場機 食餐好西<br />\n<br />\n一個星期後睇下有冇好轉<br />\n有嘅話恭喜你 繼續撐落去<br />\n轉變唔大嘅唔洗灰心<br />\n我相信你已經做咗俾平時多<br />\n都好值得加許<br />\n不過可能要搵個人督促下你<br />\n我諗約咗人應該唔會放飛機嘅"},{"pid":"da65126d7f095c1cb6199ca457d6c8485d2cc198","tid":868622,"uid":217685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc788326d891f0add1e0a911aa8aed08c560d0b0","tid":868622,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"62302a044d675e8551eb3777427537eeb4a1c657","tid":868622,"uid":186662,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"呢個真 懶令我失去左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:47:57.000Z","msg":"如果我發育時期肯去打籃球 應該有1.83<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：1.73<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懶撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T21:47:07.000Z","msg":"你叫啲有做運動都矮過173情何以堪呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace73c575dab2bb4a504bd2a86c7dc9d951f19c5","tid":868622,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6209366e41f385a3a485054f9e7de6a3f0f73b13","tid":868622,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f7c181ac1870e4080a8ce55141f49de475b6673","tid":868622,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ce683e8af0d3580d6e6966bb9de328c3e59e9f2","tid":868622,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"懶唔係問題<br />\n蠢先係問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但一個人聰明即使佢好懶佢係會不斷諗辦法令自己繼續懶而同樣都可以完成到件事<br />\n<br />\n相反蠢既跟本唔識諗自己做緊既方向係岩定錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-1